## Security Baseline Output Format

Include this section in `flow/references/project_analysis.md` (Step 9 of setup):

```markdown
## Security Baseline

**Posture**: {Good|Caution|Risk}
**Scanned**: {date}

### Secrets Scan
- [{PASS|WARN}] Hardcoded secrets in source files: {count found or "none"}
- [{PASS|WARN}] `.env` file gitignored: {yes|no|no .env file}
- [{PASS|INFO}] `.env.example` template: {exists|missing}

### Security Libraries
| Category | Library | Version | Status |
|----------|---------|---------|--------|
| Authentication | {lib} | {ver} | Detected |
| Password Hashing | — | — | Not detected |
| Input Validation | {lib} | {ver} | Detected |
| Security Headers | — | — | Not detected |
| Rate Limiting | — | — | Not detected |

### Recommendations
- {actionable suggestion based on gaps}
```
